chart.name: Hosts Reporting
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_connections.current', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).sum(by=['host']).count().publish(label='A')

chart.name: Sets/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_command.set', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Get Requests/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_ops.hits', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='A')
B = data('memcached_ops.misses', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: # Items
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_items.current', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Total Items
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_items.current').sum().publish(label='A')

chart.name: Hit Rate %
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_ops.hits', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('memcached_ops.misses', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/(A+B)).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Lowest Hit Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_ops.hits').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('memcached_ops.misses').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/(A+B)).bottom(count=5).scale(100).mean(by=['host']).publish(label='C')

chart.name: % Cache Used
chart.programText:
A = data('df.cache.free', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('df.cache.used', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B/(A+B)).scale(100).mean().publish(label='C')

chart.name: Items 1h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_items.current', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('memcached_items.current', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).timeshift('1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B-1).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Top hosts gets/sec
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_command.get').publish(label='A')

chart.name: Top hosts sets/sec
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_command.set').publish(label='A')

chart.name: Cache Size
chart.programText:
A = data('df.cache.free', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached') and filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).publish(label='A')
B = data('df.cache.used', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached') and filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Total Connections
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_connections.current', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).sum().publish(label='A')

chart.name: Network Bits/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_octets.tx', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).sum().scale(8).publish(label='A')
B = data('memcached_octets.rx', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).sum().scale(8).publish(label='B')

chart.name: % Cache Used
chart.programText:
A = data('df.cache.free').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('df.cache.used').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B/(A+B)).scale(100).mean().publish(label='C')

chart.name: Connections
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_connections.current', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached') and filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0')).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Network Bits/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_octets.tx').sum().scale(8).publish(label='A')
B = data('memcached_octets.rx').sum().scale(8).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Total Evictions/sec
chart.programText: A = data('memcached_ops.evictions').sum().publish(label='A')

chart.name: Hit Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_ops.hits', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('memcached_ops.misses', filter=filter('plugin', 'memcached')).sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/(A+B)).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Sets/sec vs Evictions %
chart.programText:
A = data('memcached_command.set', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='A')
B = data('memcached_ops.evictions', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-memcached-1.4.14-0') and filter('plugin', 'memcached')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (100*B/A).publish(label='C')

B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')

E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')
